Friday, July 24, 1992

MOTION DOCKET

92-1282. State ex rel. Gee v. Brown.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of relator’s request for an alternative writ,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said request for an alternative writ be, and the same is *1435hereby, denied, effective July 23, 1992.

Moyer, CJ., not participating.
